Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.73,0:10:37.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.57,0:10:40.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個叫做Brain Burst的程序
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.91,0:10:43.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能順利安裝完的話 我就告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.49,0:10:44.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順利是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.20,0:10:48.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說也有可能會失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.88,0:11:01.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\an8\fs25}歡迎來到加速世界
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.39,0:11:06.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Accelerate 加速世界
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.14,0:11:10.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想如果是你的話 應該沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.23,0:11:12.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來沒有看錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.10,0:11:16.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去的我在接受這個時
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.52,0:11:18.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還猶豫了將近2分鐘呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.32,0:11:22.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來為了說服你而準備的台詞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.32,0:11:23.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經白費了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.95,0:11:26.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你個傢伙 有田！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.79,0:11:30.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別給我躲 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.54,0:11:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶油菠蘿包和草莓酸奶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.75,0:11:35.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.42,0:11:38.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你貌似是…荒谷君對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.34,0:11:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從有田君那裡聽說過你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.80,0:11:48.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說你 是不是從動物園搞錯才送到這個中學來的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.72,0:11:50.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉…等…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.98,0:11:53.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.56,0:11:59.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 你這混賬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.69,0:12:02.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這頭豬！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.28,0:12:03.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是現在 喊出來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.16,0:12:05.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超頻連線
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.16,0:12:05.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(424,430)}<Burst Link>
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.74,0:12:07.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超頻連線
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.74,0:12:07.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(424,430)}<Burst Link>
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.63,0:12:26.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼情況
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.89,0:12:28.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要太注意看我的腳哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.56,0:12:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這個位置勉勉強強地在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.90,0:12:33.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攝像頭的視野範圍內
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.23,0:12:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…這到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.52,0:12:40.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在正處於Brain Buster的機能下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.61,0:12:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在加速…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.44,0:12:43.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加速？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.57,0:12:46.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 這裡就是 [加速世界]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.66,0:12:49.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們超頻連線者生存的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.66,0:12:49.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(389,430)}<Buster Linker>
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.45,0:12:51.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超頻連線者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.45,0:12:51.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(424,430)}<Buster Linker>
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.66,0:12:53.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加速世界是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.97,0:13:15.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周圍的景物乍看之下貌似是停止的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.02,0:13:15.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可事實上並不是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.35,0:13:21.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個藍色的世界是由在大廳裡設置的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.86,0:13:24.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多個公共攝像機所拍攝出來的圖像
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.15,0:13:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加工合成產生的3D影像
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.32,0:13:30.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這個影像通過 神經連接終端
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.32,0:13:30.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(521,430)}<Neural Linker>
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.41,0:13:33.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳遞給加速思考的大腦 就是我們現在所看到的這個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.20,0:13:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思考竟然會加速？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.04,0:13:39.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其加速率是平常的一千倍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.96,0:13:43.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說日常的1秒化為1000秒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.55,0:13:46.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說化為16分40秒的體感時間
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.88,0:13:49.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.97,0:13:53.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要使用這份力量的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.72,0:13:56.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就快要被打的你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.60,0:13:58.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也會在那致命的一瞬間加速
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.02,0:14:02.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這超長的思考時間內將現狀給掌握分析
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.15,0:14:07.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊 本以為絕對不可能躲開的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.86,0:14:10.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 不要躲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.16,0:14:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就被他打個一拳怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.83,0:14:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春雪君
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.20,0:14:20.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要這樣 那樣 不是會很疼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.58,0:14:22.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是個機會
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.38,0:14:27.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個學生總是躲在公共攝像機的死角里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.21,0:14:28.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得以躲避處分
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.88,0:14:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是現在處於攝像機和被周圍人注視的情況下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.47,0:14:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被我挑撥了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.68,0:14:37.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反擊的機會只剩下現在了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.68,0:14:43.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我可以用Brain Buster打贏他嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.11,0:14:45.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對可以
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.48,0:14:46.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你現在已經是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.78,0:14:50.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擁有超越常人力量的超頻連線者了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.78,0:14:50.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(526,430)}<Buster Linker>
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.28,0:14:56.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 還是算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.70,0:14:58.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會老老實實挨打的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.83,0:15:00.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟是難得的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.58,0:15:04.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明智的抉擇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.75,0:15:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得的機會 我們就把他最大化吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.09,0:15:08.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.88,0:15:12.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等加速結束之後 你就向自己的後方跳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.51,0:15:14.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但…但是學姐你不就坐在那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.22,0:15:17.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說過把效果最大化嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.02,0:15:19.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經考慮好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.77,0:15:20.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.27,0:15:23.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那好好幹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.19,0:15:25.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 好…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.48,0:15:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Burst Out
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.61,0:15:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Burst Out
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.62,0:15:40.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.71,0:15:48.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.88,0:15:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師 老師！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.84,0:15:55.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.72,0:15:56.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要動
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.85,0:15:57.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…但是血…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.81,0:16:00.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心 只是劃傷而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.81,0:16:03.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說過了嗎 要將效果最大化
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.44,0:16:05.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下 荒谷就絕不會
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.25,0:16:06.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你的面前再次出現
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.02,0:16:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再也不會
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.73,0:16:14.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍耐的好 之後請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.78,0:16:15.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春雪君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.66,0:16:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有句話忘記說了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.83,0:16:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到明天上課為止
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.92,0:16:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不要把神經連接終端摘下來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.92,0:16:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(452,430)}<Neural Linker>
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.96,0:16:30.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且1秒都不可以 上全局網
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.92,0:16:33.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對 絕對的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.34,0:16:39.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs25\shad0\move(600,3,600,235[,0,720])}要切斷[全局網]嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.94,0:16:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.44,0:16:50.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中午的事情我聽說了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.69,0:16:52.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中午？ 啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.19,0:16:55.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說你被那傢伙打飛了好遠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.91,0:16:57.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 恩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.70,0:16:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傷是那時候的？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.41,0:17:02.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那傷 就是那時弄的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.70,0:17:03.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.37,0:17:06.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 只是稍微擦到點皮而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.92,0:17:08.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.88,0:17:14.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說你和二年級的黑雪姬學姐直接連接了 真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.55,0:17:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.01,0:17:19.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.02,0:17:26.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 比起這個 昨天那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.35,0:17:26.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.02,0:17:28.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春 小千
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.23,0:17:32.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小拓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.48,0:17:35.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太巧了 回家路上？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.28,0:17:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說話來 小拓之前的劍道大會我看了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.54,0:17:47.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太厲害了 一年級就已經拿了冠軍了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.33,0:17:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 只是人品好點罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.88,0:17:54.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 小千也帶了手制便當來給我加油了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.26,0:17:56.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那氣場是便當的力量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.88,0:17:58.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.38,0:18:02.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 昨天小春你也吃了小千的手制便當了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.48,0:18:09.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他為什麼會知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.73,0:18:13.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我帶便當是小拓的主意？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.57,0:18:16.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 為什麼小拓會？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.49,0:18:20.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 小千說了嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.82,0:18:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荒谷的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.49,0:18:24.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以小拓才會叫小春給我帶便當…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.83,0:18:27.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 小春！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.50,0:18:29.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.58,0:18:31.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛好有個想看的節目
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.92,0:18:33.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小拓 明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.22,0:18:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被小拓知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.03,0:18:59.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易荒谷才從我的眼前消失
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.07,0:19:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 就是這樣而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.58,0:19:06.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的現實…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.13,0:19:16.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別用那種眼神看我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.89,0:19:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經受夠這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.72,0:19:27.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我帶走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.31,0:19:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去你那啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.97,0:19:31.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想飛 飛到世界的另一頭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.60,0:19:35.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是你的願望嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.65,0:19:44.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺做了一個很奇怪的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.33,0:19:49.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那到底是什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.16,0:19:53.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老媽 午餐費
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.04,0:19:58.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春雪 你的連接斷掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.67,0:20:01.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs25\fad(500,500)}[全局網]連接中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.68,0:20:05.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.12,0:20:34.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加速了？…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.21,0:20:43.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,800)\an8\fs25}新挑戰者現身！！
