Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.95,0:21:07.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.83,0:21:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.09,0:21:29.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.39,0:21:39.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時隔好久的世紀末舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.27,0:21:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.11,0:21:44.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對手還是難得的亮晶晶的菜鳥
